OL,5,CThis Evening and Tonight:FA few
OL,6,Fshowers continuing this evening in the
OL,7,Feast, but skies will be clearing from
OL,8,Fthe west and the night will be dry
OL,9,Fwith some clear spells, localised low
OL,10,Fcloud.
OL,11,
OL,12,CTuesday:FLow cloud burning off then a
OL,13,Fdry bright day with some sunny spells.
OL,14,
OL,15,COutlook for Wednesday to Friday:
OL,16,FWednesday will be sunny and very warm.
OL,17,FSunny, hot Thursday, perhaps some
OL,18,Fthundery showers later. Showery on
OL,19,FFriday, less warm.
